The rise of Bernie Sanders and his #feelthebern hashtag clan caught many by surprise, and none more than the party establishments.
So, how did Bernie Sanders build his support, and in short order, restructure the Democratic Party?
In sum, Bernie Sanders appeared noble and sure-footed, and spoke to pressing issues affecting an ever-growing lot of Americans.
For example, Bernie Sanders and many of his devoted Berners echo Trump’s false tweets about rigged elections.
To recap, Bernie Sanders’ policy priorities are what have captivated my generation.